result.name: Wing Fat Restaurant

reviews.text: Why should I hate this restaurant? It is in fact a restaurant that offers a wide variety of food, especially, afternoon tea. I enjoy it very much.
Sincere and quality food, worth the little more dollars....
The pork chop noodle is one of the best in Causeway Bay.

Best place in the district for local traditional Chinese meal. Locals usually order set meals for breakfast, lunch and afternoon tea. And you can have a wide variety of delicious dishes during dinner time. Highly recommend the  “minced pork on egg plant with teriyaki sauce” and “crispy chicken”. And the staffs are very friendly.
Great service. No rushing like most similar places.

result.name: 榮發餐廳

reviews.text:
榮發餐廳位於天后電器道，食品種類繁多，繁忙時段要找個位置也不容易。
食品供應速度快及美味，員工服務態度也好。
Why should I hate this restaurant? It is in fact a restaurant that offers a wide variety of food, especially, afternoon tea. I enjoy it very much.
店舖面積不算大，但整潔舒適，食物質數及烹調都很好，服務態度親切友善。
食物味道不錯；下午茶餐的份量太少；鹹魚雞粒炒飯連半飽都沒有＄42，炸魚柳餐小＋薄＄39，下次過路都不入了
Sincere and quality food, worth the little more dollars....
